Genesis, Original.

First artwork featured in my very first collection **Exordium Initium**. Beginning of beginnings. 

Aestas Arbores - Latin for summer trees. This originated from a film photo I took using expired film, then this artwork was made with the assistance of generative adversarial networks, or GAN.
